title: Daily Wire Backstage: The State Of The Union Address
description:
Can President Biden do the impossible and convincingly sell his disastrous first year as a win? With Ukraine fighting for its survival, how long before China makes a move on Taiwan? After saving the internet in Ukraine with his Starlink satellites, will Elon Musk finally take a break from being the absolute best? 
Join this roundtable discussion featuring Ben Shapiro, Candace Owens, Andrew Klavan, Michael Knowles, Matt Walsh, and Daily Wire god-king Jeremy Boreing to find out!
Stay tuned for Ben Shapiro’s “The Real State Of Union” response immediately following Biden’s speech!
